des:
Find answers to your Kansas Real Estate questions when you enable this skill. Once enabled here are a few ways to use the skill: 

"Alexa, ask Kansas Real Estate how to update my name or contact information with the Commission"

"Alexa, ask Kansas Real Estate how I re-activate my license"

"Alexa, ask Kansas Real Estate where their office is located"

This is the same information the Kansas State Real Estate Commission provides through other means and is true and complete to the best of our knowledge.
